OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy on Monday but otherwise dry
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Remaining
OL,8,Fquite warm for most but becoming
OL,9,Fcooler along the east coast.
